%% Diagram: Client debounce + AbortController sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant I as Input
    participant D as Debouncer (250ms)
    participant A as AbortController
    participant API as Suggestion API

    U->>I: keystroke "p"
    I->>D: schedule(250ms)
    U->>I: keystroke "pr" (90ms later)
    I->>D: cancel + reschedule(250ms)
    U->>I: keystroke "pro" (90ms later)
    I->>D: cancel + reschedule(250ms)
    U->>I: keystroke "prog" (90ms later)
    I->>D: cancel + reschedule(250ms)

    Note over U,I: typing pause > 250ms

    D->>A: signal = new AbortController()
    D->>API: GET /suggestions?q=prog (signal)
    API-->>D: 200 top-N

    U->>I: keystroke "progr" (later)
    I->>D: schedule(250ms)
    Note over D,A: previous request still in flight
    D->>A: abort() previous request
    D->>A: new signal
    D->>API: GET /suggestions?q=progr (signal)
    API-->>D: 200 top-N
    D->>I: render top-N for "progr"
